@node "menu" "What does it do?"
@toc "menu"


                           =WHAT DOES IT DO???=

  This door is a COOL replacement for your 'G' Command in AMIEXPRESS3.XX
       any user can write REAL eall msgs preserved he has uploaded a
   certain amount of bytes or he has a cool level (all to be configured)
         It will cost him some bytes to place his eall messages :)

           THE OUTFIT IS FULL CONFIGURABLE BY THE SYSOP HIMSELF
           ----------------------------------------------------
                 It is very simple but unbelievably Coo| !


                            @{" BACK TO MAIN MENU? " link "MAIN"}

@endnode

@node "menu2" "Installation"
@toc "menu"


                            ../INSTALLATION\..

          Nice Question ! Just Copy all files to your directories
                                and go ...


                  Put this shit in your startup sequence

                               rpstart >nil:
                              rexxmast >nil:

                      *do not 4get to copy the libs*

      IF YOU DONT GET THE INSTALLATION JUST *CLOSE* YOUR BBS!DUMMASS!

@endnode

